CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: EzFill Holdings Inc is an application based mobile-fueling company. It provides fuel-delivery on-demand or in subscription to fill customer vehicles on routine intervals for the consumer, fleet, marine, and other specialty markets. EzFill's app-based platform brings the gas station to customers with a growing fleet of EzFill-branded, Mobile Fueling Trucks.
